narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: El Proyecto Del Barrio Inc. is a Clinic/Center  Federally Qualified Health Center (FQHC) provider based in Baldwin Park, CA. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $102.0M in Medicaid payments across 1.3M claims serving 0 beneficiaries.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: This provider received $102.0M in taxpayer-funded Medicaid payments — enough to fund healthcare for approximately 12,750 Medicaid beneficiaries for a full year at average per-enrollee costs.
